        "response": {
          "bodySize": 2159,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 2159,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01UX7k1GL3HuGu1zTaQJ9feT\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Let's start building your ad! I drafted a few headlines and descriptions that meet Google's requirements.\\n\\nGoogle will mix and match them to find what performs best. We can tailor them together to make them feel just right for you.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"headlines\\\": [\\n    \\\"Stop Scheduling Back-and-Forth\\\",\\n    \\\"Find Meeting Times in Seconds\\\",\\n    \\\"Meetings Across Time Zones?\\\",\\n    \\\"Auto-Schedule for Remote Teams\\\",\\n    \\\"80% Less Coordination Time\\\",\\n    \\\"Smart Calendar Scheduling Tool\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"descriptions\\\": [\\n    \\\"Connect calendars, set preferences, done. We find times that work for everyone instantly. No more Slack threads.\\\",\\n    \\\"Used by 2,000+ teams saving 15 hours weekly. Eliminate meeting coordination chaos today. Get started free.\\\",\\n    \\\"Trusted by distributed companies worldwide. Automatic scheduling across all time zones. See how much time you'll save.\\\",\\n    \\\"Stop wasting time on scheduling. Our AI suggests optimal meeting times your team just clicks to confirm.\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\n---\\n\\n**What's next?**\\n\\nThese assets are ready to plug into your Google Ads campaign! Here's what I recommend:\\n\\n1. **Test them**: Google will automatically test different combinations of headlines and descriptions to see which resonate best with your audience\\n2. **Monitor performance**: Track which headlines and descriptions get the highest click-through rates (CTR)\\n3. **Iterate**: Once you see what's working, we can refine and create new variations to improve results\\n\\nWould you like me to help you with:\\n- **Ad extensions** (callout extensions, structured snippets, or sitelink extensions)?\\n- **Landing page optimization** to match these ads?\\n- **Bidding strategy** recommendations for your campaign?\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1591,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":406,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
