          "url": "https://api.anthropic.com/v1/messages"
        },
        "response": {
          "bodySize": 1488,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1488,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01CnYxXAMUhFKKA7bCBRQDuz\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I've suggested a few keywords your audience is likely searching for when your ad appears.\\n\\nHow do these sound to you?\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"keywords\\\": [\\n    \\\"meeting scheduling tool for remote teams\\\",\\n    \\\"automatic calendar coordination software\\\",\\n    \\\"find meeting time across time zones\\\",\\n    \\\"team scheduling software\\\",\\n    \\\"meeting scheduler for distributed teams\\\",\\n    \\\"calendar sync for global teams\\\",\\n    \\\"best scheduling tool for remote work\\\",\\n    \\\"eliminate meeting coordination emails\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\nThese keywords target:\\n- **High-intent transactional** (keywords 1, 4, 5): People actively searching for scheduling solutions\\n- **Problem-focused** (keywords 3, 8): Teams frustrated with current coordination methods\\n- **Awareness/comparison** (keywords 2, 6, 7): People researching options and best practices\\n\\nThe keywords emphasize your core value propositions: **automation**, **time zone handling**, and **remote team focus**—exactly what your target audience is searching for when they're tired of endless scheduling back-and-forths.\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":992,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":244,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
