            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1289,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_0116ZjgmsMrJwrG62y8Lx4QL\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I've suggested a few keywords your audience is likely searching for when your ad appears.\\n\\nHow do these sound to you?\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"keywords\\\": [\\n    \\\"meeting scheduler for remote teams\\\",\\n    \\\"automatic scheduling across time zones\\\",\\n    \\\"calendar coordination tool\\\",\\n    \\\"find meeting times instantly\\\",\\n    \\\"distributed team scheduling software\\\",\\n    \\\"time zone meeting scheduler\\\",\\n    \\\"eliminate scheduling back and forth\\\",\\n    \\\"team calendar management tool\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\nThese keywords target:\\n- **High-intent transactional** (keywords 2, 4, 6): People actively searching for scheduling solutions\\n- **Problem-focused** (keywords 1, 3, 7): Teams frustrated with current scheduling pain\\n- **Feature-specific** (keywords 5, 8): Distributed teams and calendar management needs\\n\\nReady to review these, or would you like me to adjust the focus?\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1661,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":206,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
