            "size": 1614,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01TfpvrrEgykx9EUJtuXhB9h\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I've suggested a few keywords your audience is likely searching for when your ad appears.\\n\\nHow do these sound to you?\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"keywords\\\": [\\n    \\\"meeting scheduling tool\\\",\\n    \\\"find meeting times across time zones\\\",\\n    \\\"team calendar coordination software\\\",\\n    \\\"automatic meeting scheduler\\\",\\n    \\\"remote team scheduling solution\\\",\\n    \\\"calendar sync for distributed teams\\\",\\n    \\\"eliminate scheduling conflicts\\\",\\n    \\\"best scheduling tool for remote teams\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\nThese keywords target:\\n- **High-intent transactional**: \\\"meeting scheduling tool\\\", \\\"automatic meeting scheduler\\\", \\\"team calendar coordination software\\\"\\n- **Problem-focused**: \\\"find meeting times across time zones\\\", \\\"eliminate scheduling conflicts\\\"\\n- **Awareness & comparison**: \\\"best scheduling tool for remote teams\\\", \\\"remote team scheduling solution\\\"\\n- **Solution-oriented**: \\\"calendar sync for distributed teams\\\"\\n\\nThey align perfectly with your approved headlines and descriptions, focusing on the pain point (scheduling chaos across time zones) and your solution (automatic, instant coordination).\\n\\nReady to move forward with these, or would you like me to adjust any?\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1660,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":248,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
