          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1268,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01BzmbFBqtGNZ6NWzHSt1ojV\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I've suggested a few keywords your audience is likely searching for when your ad appears.\\n\\nHow do these sound to you?\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"keywords\\\": [\\n    \\\"meeting scheduler for remote teams\\\",\\n    \\\"find meeting time across time zones\\\",\\n    \\\"automatic calendar scheduling tool\\\",\\n    \\\"team scheduling software\\\",\\n    \\\"meeting coordination software\\\",\\n    \\\"best scheduling tool for distributed teams\\\",\\n    \\\"calendar coordination app\\\",\\n    \\\"eliminate scheduling conflicts\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\nThese keywords target the exact pain points your customers are searching for—from the practical (\\\"meeting scheduler for remote teams\\\") to the problem-focused (\\\"eliminate scheduling conflicts\\\"). They should pull in high-intent prospects who are actively looking for a solution like yours.\\n\\nWant to adjust any of these, or shall we move forward?\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1680,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":177,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
